{
  "stem": "802.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Actually, the DP camp was there, because there was some sort of a-- I think, a-- something for soldiers, German soldiers before.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we stayed with this family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The man had been a Nazi, but denied it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we knew, because he talked about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said he had no choice, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was difficult to live with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, you know, it's so interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had two rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had a large apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That-- I don't remember hating them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I remember, the food was extremely scarce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I mean, you know, we were not starving anymore, because we had packages from UNRRA, you know, and packages of food from the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we're not starving anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we used to share the food with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, in fact, my cousin established a relationship with that man's wife.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't mean a-- I don't mean a sexual [LAUGHS] relationship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Just-- she was much older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and then I worked for UNRRA in a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we separated from our cousins, because there were, you know, there was some-- there was some tension.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then ultimately, we came to the United States, and it took us 2 and 1/2 years to get affidavits.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We had relatives in the United States, but it was extremely difficult to secure papers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- we-- we kind of languished in these awful places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't awful to live with the Germans, but it was in some way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hope I don't sound quixotic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hope you don't think me mad, because some people may.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember, distinctly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a sunny day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hated the German with a passion that I cannot describe.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
